Carboxymethyl chitosan (≥90% deacetylation) was dissolved with hydrogen-rich water solution at 60 °C with stirring. The PER-CDs powder was added to the chitosan coating solution and stirred for 10 min, and high-speed shearing for 8 min at 12 000 r/min to obtain CS/PER-CDs coating solutions with PER-CDs concentrations of 1%, 2%, and 3% (

                              ω

                        ).
